desc:s3g Layout Panner
tags: multichannel spatial generic layout panner

slider1:0<0,7,1{Quad,Octophonic Ring,8ch Cube,12ch Ring,16ch Ring,16ch Double Ring,20ch Double Ring,24ch Dome No Overhead}>Speaker layout
slider2:1<0.25,4,0.01>Layout focus
slider3:6<0,48,0.1>Distance rolloff (dB/oct)
slider4:35<1,250,1>Motion smoothing (ms)
slider5:0<-360,360,0.1>Global azimuth (deg)
slider6:0<-90,90,0.1>Global elevation (deg)
slider7:0<-3,3,0.01>Global distance offset (radius)
slider8:0<-48,24,0.1>Output gain (dB)
slider9:35<0,100,1>Distance diffusion (%)

slider10:0<-360,360,0.1>S1 azimuth (deg)
slider11:0<-90,90,0.1>S1 elevation (deg)
slider12:1<0.1,3,0.01>S1 distance (radius, edge=1)
slider13:45<-360,360,0.1>S2 azimuth (deg)
